rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I fled to Acedia and made a new life
for myself here. How many years
has it been now...?

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Interested, are you? There's not much
to say. I get out of bed, get my rations,
wander about for a bit, then sleep.

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Everyone blames Superbia for
annexing Gula, and- Wait, are
those Blades with you?!

rows.label: tlk41400071_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Those Blades burned my house down,
destroyed everything I loved! Down
with Blades! Down with them, I say!
